textbox_5.text: I think I mainly went by how easily I could distinguish the two colors, that they weren't just shades of the same or similar colors. For example two blues can be very different.
textbox_7.text:
Since I found most examples very different I was thinking that I maybe had misunderstood the instructions, but I don't anymore.

P.S. Forcing a maximized window is annoying if the user has a large screen! At least if you display text on it, centered at that. Hard to read very loooong centered lines. Just sayin'. ;-)
